I promise you.

40:44.233 --> 40:45.693
Listen, um...

40:47.236 --> 40:51.949
I have to tell you,
I went and had dinner with Stacie.

40:52.032 --> 40:55.744
-How did that go?
-She told me that Mark's mom, Cassandra...

40:56.787 --> 41:00.875
-wants custody of my embryos.
-Oh, come on. Is that even a thing?

41:00.958 --> 41:04.086
