So if she finds out,
she's gonna want custody of the baby?

41:12.845 --> 41:13.971
I don't know.

41:14.054 --> 41:16.140
If it turns out to be Mark's baby--

41:16.223 --> 41:18.434
Think she'd go through
with something like that?

41:18.517 --> 41:21.145
I don't know.
But when Cassandra wants something,

41:21.228 --> 41:24.356
she will do anything she can to get it.

41:36.494 --> 41:39.622
-Here it is.
-Yeah, yeah, yeah. We'll wait for backup.

41:39.705 --> 41:42.208
-Well, where are they?
-I gave out the coordinates.

41:42.291 --> 41:43.501
Should be here any minute.

41:47.671 --> 41:48.881
I don't see anyone.

41:50.132 --> 41:51.091
Hey, look.

41:53.761 --> 41:54.595
Is that Calvin?

41:57.973 --> 41:58.807
Yeah.

42:03.771 --> 42:06.398
Howard, where the hell's backup?
Got eyes on Calvin.

42:06.482 --> 42:09.485
<i>We're closing in now.</i>
